<section id="contact" class="w-full bg-[#456a44] py-12 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-8 relative z-50 overflow-hidden">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative">
		<!-- Leaf Decoration - Right Side -->
		<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1/4 md:w-1/3 opacity-30 z-0 hidden md:block">
			<img 
				src="/images/contact-section/leaf.svg" 
				alt="Decorative leaf illustration" 
				class="w-full h-full object-contain object-right"
				loading="lazy"
				width="400"
				height="600"
			/>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 relative z-10">
			<!-- Left Column - Contact Form -->
			<div>
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#fff8ed] mb-4">
					How can we help you today?
				</h2>
				<p class="text-white mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
					We are excited to discover how our support can positively impact you. Please fill out the form, and we will get in touch with you as soon as possible.
				</p>
				
				<!-- Google Form Embed -->
				<div class="w-full">
					<iframe 
						src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfZBaXk_acxzDea9E_WTkhqkZH2X5nLN1LQOszeJoQ_hSG1Mw/viewform?embedded=true" 
						width="100%" 
						height="875" 
						frameborder="0" 
						marginheight="0" 
						marginwidth="0"
						class="w-full"
					>
						Loading…
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Right Column - Information Section -->
			<div>
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
					Schedule a tour today!
				</h2>
				<p class="text-white mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
					Embark on a journey of care, comfort, ​and community at Horminy Adult ​Foster Care Home. Our dedicated ​team understands the importance of ​finding the perfect place where your ​loved ones can thrive, and we're here ​to provide just that. Nestled in a ​tranquil environment, our home offers ​personalized support tailored to each ​individual's needs, ensuring they feel ​cherished and valued every step of ​the way. From cozy living spaces to ​engaging activities and ​compassionate caregivers, we strive ​to create a warm and inviting ​atmosphere that feels just like home. ​Schedule a tour today and let us ​show you why Horminy Adult Foster ​Care Home is the ideal place for your ​family member to call home.</p>

